ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It is a history course covering the independence era across the African continent. I would recommend it if they have a background in African history.
I would recommend it as a good overview for decolonization and independence in Africa.
